panels.title: 成交-食物

targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
    date_bin('2 seconds'::INTERVAL, timestamp) as time_window,
    product_id,
    COUNT(*) as trade_count
FROM public.trade_logs 
WHERE price > 0.0 
    AND task_id = '${task_id}'
    AND product_category = 'Food'
GROUP BY date_bin('2 seconds'::INTERVAL, timestamp),product_id
ORDER BY time_window

panels.title: 成交量分析-食物

targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
    date_bin('1 seconds'::INTERVAL, timestamp) as time_window,
    product_id,
    AVG(price) AS price
FROM public.trade_logs 
WHERE price > 0.0 
    AND task_id = '${task_id}'
    AND product_category = 'Food'
GROUP BY date_bin('1 seconds'::INTERVAL, timestamp),product_id
ORDER BY time_window

panels.title: 成交价变化曲线-食物

targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
    date_bin('1 seconds'::INTERVAL, timestamp) as time_window,
    product_id,
    sum(price) AS amount
FROM public.trade_logs 
WHERE price > 0.0 
    AND task_id = '${task_id}'
    AND product_category = 'Food'
GROUP BY date_bin('1 seconds'::INTERVAL, timestamp),product_id
ORDER BY time_window

panels.title: 分商品贸易额变化曲线-食物

targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
    date_bin('2 seconds'::INTERVAL, timestamp) as time_window,
    product_id,
    COUNT(CASE WHEN trade_result = 'Success' THEN 1 END) as Success,
    COUNT(CASE WHEN trade_result = 'Failed' THEN 1 END) as Failed,
    COUNT(CASE WHEN trade_result = 'NotMatched' THEN 1 END) as NotMatched,
    COUNT(CASE WHEN trade_result = 'NotYet' THEN 1 END) as NotYet,
FROM public.trade_logs 
WHERE  task_id = '${task_id}' AND product_category = 'Food'
GROUP BY date_bin('2 seconds'::INTERVAL, timestamp),product_id;

panels.title: 交易量分交易结果图表

targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
    date_bin('2 seconds'::INTERVAL, timestamp) as time_window,
    COUNT(CASE WHEN interval_relation = 'Overlapping' THEN 1 END) as Over_lapping,
    COUNT(CASE WHEN interval_relation = 'AgentBelowFactory' THEN 1 END) as Agent_Below_Factory,
    COUNT(CASE WHEN interval_relation = 'AgentAboveFactory' THEN 1 END) as Agent_Above_Factory,
FROM public.trade_logs 
WHERE  task_id = '${task_id}' AND product_category = 'Food'
GROUP BY date_bin('2 seconds'::INTERVAL, timestamp)

    date_bin('2 seconds'::INTERVAL, timestamp) as time_window,
    avg(agent_pref_current_range_upper) as max_upper,
    avg(agent_pref_current_range_lower) AS min_lower
FROM public.trade_logs 
WHERE price > 0.0 
    AND task_id = '${task_id}'
GROUP BY date_bin('2 seconds'::INTERVAL, timestamp)
ORDER BY time_window

    sum(cash)
FROM public.agent_cash_logs

targets.rawSql:
